        "goseg/config/version.go and goseg/startram/startram.go both use package-level mutable state (`VersionInfo`, `VersionServerReady`, `Regions`, `EventBus`) that is written by sync paths and read elsewhere, creating implicit cross-module contracts instead of explicit interfaces.",
        "goseg/handler/upload.go depends directly on importer side-effect functions (`SetUploadSession`, `Reset`) keyed by string action values, coupling handler behavior to importer internals without an explicit boundary contract object."
